 💡 Key Insights

- Communication and Social categories have the highest number of installs.
- Most applications on the Google Play Store are free.
- Highly rated apps generally receive more installs.
- Paid apps represent a small portion of the market but can generate significant revenue in selected categories.
- User sentiment is mostly positive for highly rated applications.


